column3:
The spread operator works only on iterable objects and arrays. Write the code to copy the first object into the other variable, and add a property "extra" with a value of 20.
let jsonified_data = {one: 1, two: 2};
let new_data = {};
column4:
let jsonified_data = {one: 1, two: 2};
let new_data = {...jsonified_data, extra: 20};
